<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Foremost" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Foremost,</orth> 1) going before others, most advanced: <cit><quote>thou goest f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.162" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 162</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my wife comes f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 22</bibl></cit>.
<lb />2) first in place and dignity: <cit><quote>goes f. in report,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 97</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you shall have f. hand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.2.140" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 2, 140</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the f. man of all this world,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 22</bibl></cit>.
<pb n="442" />
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>